title: Versartis: 1Q Earnings Snapshot
text:
MENLO PARK, Calif. (AP) _ Versartis Inc. (VSAR) on Tuesday reported a loss of $9 million in its first quarter.
The Menlo Park, California-based company said it had a loss of 25 cents per share.
The company's shares closed at $1.50. A year ago, they were trading at $17.50.
